{"tid":236612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）偽娘太性感撩人，網友傳自拍J照約炮","createTime":"2017-05-10T00:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T01:42:10.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d36d795558d5f96ad9d5b9ea9b5b9c8f187c8079","tid":236612,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:14:48.000Z","msg":"偽娘太性感 網友傳鳥照想約炮<br />\n<br />\n日本一名偽娘Coser&ldquo;Do~u&rarr;tama&rdquo;，因火辣性感的打扮，加上魔鬼身材，乍看之下比許多女生還像女生。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有不少網友追蹤，但除了一般欣賞的粉絲之外，還有許多居心不良的粉絲，傳自己的下體照想要約炮，讓他飽受困擾。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Do~u&rarr;tama&rdquo;日前在推特發文談自己的困擾時，表示雖然自己很開心能受到粉絲的喜歡，但日本的網友傳給他的訊息，很多都是性騷擾的留言，或者是直接傳自己的下體照，問他要不要約炮，反觀國外的粉絲傳的訊息，則是稱讚他很正、很性感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/20170509/%E5%81%BD%E5%A8%98%E5%A4%AA%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%82%B3%E9%B3%A5%E7%85%A7%E6%83%B3%E7%B4%84%E7%82%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2F20170509%2F%25E5%2581%25BD%25E5%25A8%2598%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259F-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%25B3%25A5%25E7%2585%25A7%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%2582%25AE%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=57187eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinapress.com.my/20170509/%E5%81%BD%E5%A8%98%E5%A4%AA%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%82%B3%E9%B3%A5%E7%85%A7%E6%83%B3%E7%B4%84%E7%82%AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1frghd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1frghd.jpg&h=4cda4035&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/081438_103e405bac47e51025c3805d4d213d27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F081438_103e405bac47e51025c3805d4d213d27.jpg&h=9242e3db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45d478c56fd9040d88c7486887c1aa20851ccc49","tid":236612,"uid":106760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:30:53.000Z","msg":"男人老狗條丁細到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3bdfd1feba79e5cc63fd45ffc03740fb91668c","tid":236612,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d085525f176bd6a646f02e4fa9e1208e6a3877","tid":236612,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T01:42:10.000Z","msg":"正在邊度"}]}